# Design System — Luxury Plush Aesthetic

## Colour palette (CSS custom properties — never hard-code hex)
```css
--cream: #f7f2ea;           /* primary text, light backgrounds */
--blush: #e8c5b0;           /* secondary warm accent */
--rose: #c97b6e;            /* CTA hover, accent highlights */
--velvet: #14080f;          /* near-black rich bg variant */
--deep: #080407;            /* page background */
--gold: #c9a96e;            /* primary accent, cursor, borders */
--gold2: #e8d5a3;           /* lighter gold, tag labels */
--gold-deep: #8a7349;       /* muted gold for dividers */
--champagne: #f3e8d4;       /* card highlights */
--platinum: rgba(247,242,234,0.06); /* subtle glass tint */
--mauve: #8b5e7a;           /* story/emotional accent */
--mist: #c9b8c4;            /* inactive / muted text */
--soft-pink: #f0d5d0;       /* decorative motifs */
--shadow-luxury: 0 32px 100px rgba(0,0,0,0.55), 0 0 0 1px rgba(201,169,110,0.08) inset;
--ease-out-expo: cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1);
```

## Typography
- `--font-display: var(--font-cormorant), "Cormorant Garamond", Georgia, serif` — headings, hero, pull quotes
- `--font-body: var(--font-inter), "Inter", -apple-system, sans-serif` — body, labels, UI

### Type scale (awwwards level)
```css
/* Hero headline */
font-family: var(--font-display);
font-size: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 9rem);
font-weight: 300;
letter-spacing: -0.03em;
line-height: 0.9;

/* Section heading */
font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 5rem);
font-weight: 400;
letter-spacing: -0.02em;

/* Overline / label */
font-family: var(--font-body);
font-size: 0.65rem;
font-weight: 600;
letter-spacing: 0.2em;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(--gold2);

/* Body */
font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.5vw, 1.05rem);
font-weight: 300;
line-height: 1.7;
color: rgba(247, 242, 234, 0.7);
```

## Spacing rhythm
Use multiples of 8px: `8 16 24 32 48 64 96 128 160 200px`.
Section padding: `clamp(80px, 12vw, 160px) 0`.

## Glass morphism card
```css
.card {
  background: rgba(247, 242, 234, 0.04);
  border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.12);
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  border-radius: 2px; /* intentionally minimal */
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-luxury);
  transition: border-color 0.4s var(--ease-out-expo),
              box-shadow 0.4s var(--ease-out-expo);
}
.card:hover {
  border-color: rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.28);
  box-shadow: 0 48px 120px rgba(0,0,0,0.6), 0 0 0 1px rgba(201,169,110,0.2) inset;
}
```

## Button styles
```css
/* Primary CTA */
.btn-primary {
  background: transparent;
  border: 1px solid var(--gold);
  color: var(--cream);
  padding: 14px 36px;
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  cursor: none;
  transition: background 0.35s var(--ease-out-expo), color 0.35s;
}
.btn-primary:hover {
  background: var(--gold);
  color: var(--deep);
}
```

## Grain / ambient overlay (already in `body::before`)
Always `pointer-events: none; z-index: 0; position: fixed; opacity: 0.025`.

## Marquee text
Use `<Marquee />` component from `@/components/ui/Marquee` — do not build a new one.

## Dividers
Use `<SectionDivider />` from `@/components/ui/SectionDivider` — thin gold line, optional label.

## Image treatment
- Always provide `.webp` first, `.png` fallback
- Use `<ProgressiveImage />` for above-fold images
- `object-fit: cover` with `aspect-ratio` set on wrapper, never fixed height
- Subtle `filter: brightness(0.85) saturate(1.1)` on product images for mood

## Mobile
- Navigation: hamburger at `< 768px`, full menu at `>= 768px`
- Reduce hero font-size with `clamp()`
- Touch: disable custom cursor (`display: none` on `.cursor-dot`, `.cursor-ring`)
- Lenis: disabled on touch-only devices (already handled in provider)
